data.description: This charming move in ready Bay Ridge home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths with open floor plan. You will find the primary suite with a soaker tub, shower and walk-in closet off the kitchen allowing for privacy. On the opposite side of the house, you will find 3 bedrooms which are a nice size and offer enough space for guests along with the second full bathroom.  One of the extra bedrooms could be used as an office or extra living area. The laundry room is conveniently located on this side of the house for easy access. You will love the open kitchen with a breakfast bar and a great sized dining area that leads out to the spacious backyard (which has plenty of room for all your entertainment and grilling needs). Don’t miss this move-in ready home located conveniently near restaurants, shopping, & highly ranked schools!
